1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,347
Pause for a moment.

2
00:00:01,347 --> 00:00:03,390
Let your attention come to your breath.

3
00:00:03,390 --> 00:00:05,294
You do not need to change it.

4
00:00:05,294 --> 00:00:06,966
Just notice one inhale.

5
00:00:09,966 --> 00:00:11,220
And one exhale.

6
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:17,099
Now feel where the breath is easiest to
notice.

7
00:00:17,099 --> 00:00:18,074
Maybe the nose.

8
00:00:18,074 --> 00:00:18,863
The chest.

9
00:00:18,863 --> 00:00:19,699
The belly.

10
00:00:19,699 --> 00:00:22,021
Or the movement of your whole body.

11
00:00:22,021 --> 00:00:24,993
Let this place become your anchor.

12
00:00:24,993 --> 00:00:28,290
For the next few breaths, simply return
here.

13
00:00:28,290 --> 00:00:30,473
Breathing in, I notice.

14
00:00:33,473 --> 00:00:35,516
Breathing out, I soften.

15
00:00:35,516 --> 00:00:38,256
If your mind wanders, that is okay.

16
00:00:38,256 --> 00:00:40,532
Come back to the next breath.

17
00:00:40,532 --> 00:00:45,130
Now ask yourself: What is one part of me
that needed this pause?

18
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:51,130
<break time="3s" />

19
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:53,034
Notice the answer gently.

20
00:00:53,034 --> 00:00:54,938
Take one final breath.

21
00:00:54,938 --> 00:00:57,724
And return to your day with a little more
space.

